# ============================================================================
# Instructions for setup:
# ============================================================================
# 1. Go to your Supabase project dashboard
# 2. Navigate to Settings > API
# 3. Copy the Project URL and paste it as SUPABASE_URL
# 4. Copy the anon public key and paste it as SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# 5. Copy the service_role secret key and paste it as SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
# 6. For DATABASE_URL, go to Settings > Database and copy the connection string
# 7. Add these variables to your main .env file